content.rendered: Pusat kamera CCTV Honeywell, kami menyediakan Kamera CCTV H2W4PER3 untuk anda dengan harga murah. Kamera CCTV Honeywell H2W4PER3 sangat efektif dalam menaga keamanan rumah / kantor / gedung / dlsb. Honeywell H2W4PER3 tipe kamera pengawas yang memiliki kelebihan:Features 1/3″ 4 MP progressive scan imager 2.8 mm fixed lens True day/night (IR-cut filter) Wide dynamic range up to 120 dB Low-light performance down to 0.03/0.07 lux (color) or 0 lux with IR LEDs on Up to 66 ft (20 m) IR illumination, depending on scene reflectance H.265 Smart Codec Triple stream support Built-in microphone Support up to 128GB Micro SDHC card class 10 PoE (802.3af) or 12 VDC support Plug-and-play compatible with Honeywell Performance Series Embedded NVRs IP66 and IK10-rated rugged housing
